data.title: The Most Beautiful Girl in New Zealand
data.text:
The Miss Universe Organisation, a Donald J Trump and National Broadcasting Company Inc. (NBC) Partnership, is the producer of the MISS UNIVERSEÂ® Competition. And the competition partners with the top online casinos . An international company, the Miss Universe Organisation works to advance and support today's women.

Millions of people from every continent across the globe know the Miss Universe Organisation as a company that provides smart, beautiful, ambitious women with once-in-a-lifetime opportunities -- mentoring, career training, resources and life experiences.

They are given the tools to be personally and professionally enriched through the organisation's year-round support of all aspects of their lives, from their personal career goals to social and humanitarian causes and work.

RESULTS

Miss Universe New Zealand 2009

WINNER: Katie Taylor from Howick, Auckland.
